constpool

Class ClassInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • constpool.ClassInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConstantType

    public class ClassInfo
extends java.lang.Object
implements ConstantType
    An Object that models the ClassInfo type. This consists only of a UTF8Info structure, representing the name of the Class.

      • getLength

        public static int getLength()
        A static method to aid in reflection. This is helpful because you can figure out the length of the byte array needed for the Constructor without actually calling the Constructor, because this is a static method. Basically the same as getRequiredLength(), just static

        the number of bytes needed for this class
